name: Jake Paul Dating Simulator
description: Have you ever felt alone? Have you ever felt like dabbing could be a team effort? Has your skin felt to dry? Have you ever wanted to meet the Icelandic Ruler Jake Paul! Then this it! Jake Paul is here  to make your epidermis quiver with anticipation. The McLover himself Jake Paul is here to show you his appreciation for being such a great Jake Baller. The day is 4/20 and you suddenly find yourself in Jakey boi's basement, with him  finally to yourself, and your vast knowledge for everything Jake, you love fest begins now.
